io.doov.core.dsl.field.types

Interface TextFieldInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseFieldInfo<java.lang.String>, DslField<java.lang.String>, Readable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StringFieldInfo

    public interface TextFieldInfo
extends BaseFieldInfo<java.lang.String>
    Base interface for text field info.

    It contains default methods for common checks, which are calls to methods on StringCondition.
